---
title: Excel - convert names into email addresses
parent: Fixes
tags: [Windows, PowerShell, Active Directory]
---

## Column A is your list of names [First Last]
## Column B will be your working area.  Once formual resolves, use fill handle to pull down the rest.
=LOWER(LEFT(A1,1) & TRIM(RIGHT(SUBSTITUTE(A1," "," "),LEN(A1))) & "@hw.com;")
